:

1. *Pod* se nalazi tajni ured. (Underneath is located a secret office.)
2. *Pod* je smanjio svoju potrošnju hrane. (He decreased his food consumption.)
3. *Pod* se nalaze skrivene dragocenosti. (Beneath are hidden treasures.)
4. Ona je čvrsto stala *pod* zastavom. (She stood firmly under the flag.)
5. *Pod* je ponovo postavio svoju veru. (He restored his faith.)